[{"id":"fact.amp.numbering","kind":"fact","title":"增幅器社区编号规则","aliases":["增幅器","指挥官增幅器","177增幅器","777增幅器"],"content":"三位数字依次表示棱镜、支架、曲柄；编号是部件解锁顺序，不代表强度。1～4来自夜羽，5～7来自索拉里斯之声。","sources":[{"url":"https://wiki.warframe.com/w/Amp","label":"Warframe Wiki - Amp"}],"gameVersion":"2026-07","updatedAt":"2026-07-13","reviewStatus":"approved","reviewedBy":["12407"]},{"id":"fact.weapon.crafting-ingredients","kind":"fact","title":"作为合成材料的武器","aliases":["武器合成表","武器合成树","武器作为材料"],"content":"具体关系必须以当前 Wiki 页面为准。原料武器会被消耗，其强化项目不会继承。","sources":[{"url":"https://wiki.warframe.com/w/Weapons_Required_as_Crafting_Ingredients","label":"Warframe Wiki"}],"gameVersion":"current","updatedAt":"2026-07-13","reviewStatus":"approved","reviewedBy":["12407"]},{"id":"fact.critical.formulas","kind":"fact","title":"暴击计算公式","aliases":["暴击公式","暴击率计算","暴击倍率计算"],"content":"最终暴击率=基础暴击率×(1+相对暴击率加成总和)。最终暴击倍率=基础暴击倍率×(1+相对暴击伤害加成总和)。","sources":[{"url":"https://wiki.warframe.com/w/Critical_Hit","label":"Warframe Wiki"}],"gameVersion":"2026-07","updatedAt":"2026-07-13","reviewStatus":"approved","reviewedBy":["12407"]}]
